      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl05_LabelName\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"><sub style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary);\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\" src=\"systems/sfrpg/images/cup/gameplay/graviton.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />&nbsp;</sub></span><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl05_LabelName\">Graviton Revelation<br /></span>When you use the gravity surge revelation, you can choose to attempt a bull rush combat maneuver instead of a disarm or trip combat maneuver. You can attempt this bull rush from any direction, regardless of your position relative to the target.</p>\n<div title=\"Page 55\">\n<p>When you&rsquo;re attuned or fully attuned, if you bull rush a creature using gravity surge and that creature&rsquo;s movement would be checked by another creature of its size or smaller or by an obstacle, you attempt a trip combat maneuver against each creature as if using the gravity surge revelation. You must have the gravity surge revelation to select this revelation.</p>\n</div>"
